before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.2 Leading Debounce</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Leading Debounce</code>는 연속적인 이벤트들 중 첫번째 이벤트만 실행하도록 하는 방식이다.\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/bbbf7/image-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/a59e9/image-2.webp 192w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/0ca9f/image-2.webp 384w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/dc9b9/image-2.webp 768w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/e2c2f/image-2.webp 1152w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/94b1e/image-2.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/3b721/image-2.png 192w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/66595/image-2.png 384w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/fe486/image-2.png 768w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/d2d74/image-2.png 1152w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/bbbf7/image-2.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/fe486/image-2.png\"\n            alt=\"alt text\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n그림과 같이 처음 이벤트가 발생하면 즉시 실행되며 이후 타이머를 이용하여 이벤트가 실행되지 않도록 한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"13-debounce-hook-구현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#13-debounce-hook-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"13 debounce hook 구현 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.3 Debounce Hook 구현</h2>\n<p>다음은 입력 이벤트를 받아 Trailing Debounce를 구현한 Hook이다.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"62257461725942060000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`interface debounceProps<T> {\r\n  value: T;\r\n  delay: number;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction useDebounce<T>({ value, delay }: debounceProps<T>): T {\r\n  const [debouncedValue, setDebouncedValue] = useState(value);\r\n\r\n  useEffect(() => {\r\n    // 타이머 이후 마지막 value를 선택(Trailing Debounce)\r\n    const handler = setTimeout(() => {\r\n      setDebouncedValue(value);\r\n    }, delay);\r\n\r\n    // value가 변경 되면 타이머를 초기화\r\n    return () => {\r\n      clearTimeout(handler);\r\n    };\r\n  }, [value]);\r\n\r\n  return debouncedValue;\r\n}`, `62257461725942060000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">debounceProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  value<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  delay<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">useDebounce</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> delay <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> debounceProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>debouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setDebouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 타이머 이후 마지막 value를 선택(Trailing Debounce)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handler <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token function\">setDebouncedValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> delay<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// value가 변경 되면 타이머를 초기화</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token function\">clearTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>handler<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> debouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-throttle\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-throttle\" aria-label=\"2 throttle permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Throttle</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Throttle</code>은 한번 실행되면 일정 시간 동안 다시 실행되지 않도록 하는 기술이다.<br>\n즉, 일정 시간 간격에서 최대 1번만 이벤트가 실행되도록 한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/78ab2/image-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.645833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/a59e9/image-3.webp 192w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/0ca9f/image-3.webp 384w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/dc9b9/image-3.webp 768w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/e2c2f/image-3.webp 1152w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/c6649/image-3.webp 1201w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/3b721/image-3.png 192w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/66595/image-3.png 384w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/fe486/image-3.png 768w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/d2d74/image-3.png 1152w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/78ab2/image-3.png 1201w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/fe486/image-3.png\"\n            alt=\"alt text\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위 그림과 같이 어떤 이벤트가 발생하면 구간이 시작되며 해당 구간에서는 이벤트가 최대 1번만 실행된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"21-throttle-hook-구현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-throttle-hook-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"21 throttle hook 구현 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1 Throttle Hook 구현</h2>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"99589563649016920000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"📋  코드를 복사했습니다.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`interface throttleProps<T> {\r\n  callback: () => void;\r\n  delay: number;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 제어하고자 하는 핸들러를 callback으로 받아 throttle을 구현\r\nfunction useThrottle({ callback, delay }: throttleProps<T>): void {\r\n  const lastRun = useRef(Date.now());\r\n\r\n  return () => {\r\n    const timeElapsed = Date.now() - lastRun.current;\r\n    // 간격이후 발생한 이벤트만 실행\r\n    if(timeElapsed >= delay) {\r\n      callback();\r\n      lastRun.current = Date.now();\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}`, `99589563649016920000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></re